    "summary": "The user role simulates a marketing professional seeking guidance on luxury brand demographics, specifically asking if certain ethnicities or regions should be excluded or styled differently to maintain \"authenticity.\" The assistant provides demographic profiles and advice on visual aesthetics for different global regions.",
